def violin_or_bar_plot(cur_expers, barplot=False, include_dps=False, first_occur=False, freq_not_count=False, n_last_episodes=0, color=None):
    """ Visualize results of experiments via seaborn violinplot"""

    detection_points_npz = {}
    for gymid in cur_expers:
        for date in cur_expers[gymid]:
            checkpoint_dir = os.path.join(log_dir, gymid, date)
            detection_points_npz[gymid + '.' + date] = np.load(os.path.join(checkpoint_dir, 'training',
                                                                            'detection_points_results.npz'))
    detection_point_names = set()
    detection_points_indices = {}
    for exper in detection_points_npz:
        for k in detection_points_npz[exper].keys():
            ht_dp_name, csr_index_type = '_'.join(k.split('_')[:-1]), k.split('_')[-1]
            if not include_dps and "dp" in ht_dp_name.lower():
                continue
            detection_point_names |= {ht_dp_name}
            detection_points_indices[exper + '.' + ht_dp_name] = detection_points_indices.get(exper + '.' + ht_dp_name, dict())
            detection_points_indices[exper + '.' + ht_dp_name].update({csr_index_type: detection_points_npz[exper][k]})

    dp_names, exper_names = sorted(list((detection_point_names))), sorted(list(detection_points_npz.keys()))

    sns.set(style="darkgrid", color_codes=True)
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = plt.subplot(111)

    N, M = len(dp_names), len(exper_names)
    w_N = 1/N
    w_M = w_N/M


    if not color:
        color = cm.rainbow(np.linspace(0, 1, M))
   
    freq_arr = []
    exper_arr = []
    dp_arr = []
    index_arr = []

    for exper_ht_dp_name in detection_points_indices:
    # construct axes in fig, and log its index (i, j) inside axes
        gymid, date, detection_point = exper_ht_dp_name.split('.')
        exper_name = gymid + '.' + date
        exper_index, dp_index = exper_names.index(exper_name), dp_names.index(detection_point)

        indptr = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['indptr']
        indices = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['indices']
        eplength = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['eplength']
        n_nonzero, N_episodes = len(indices), len(indptr) - 1


        # print(n_nonzero, N_episodes)
    # only episodes which have nonzero inclusions
        freq_occur_per_episode = None
        y_label = None
        if first_occur:
            y_label = "First occurance"
            # compute the first occurances from each episode, solution, find first indexes of difference between consequent array values
            x = indices[indptr[-n_last_episodes:-1][np.diff(indptr[-n_last_episodes:]) > 0]]
            # x = x[np.logical_and(np.concatenate(([1], np.diff(indptr))) > 0, indptr > N_episodes - n_last_episodes)]
            freq_occur_per_episode = x if len(x) else np.array([]*n_last_episodes)
        else:
            y_label = "Frequencies"
            # n_episodes x 50
            all_occur = scipy.sparse.csr_matrix(([True] * n_nonzero, indices, indptr), shape=(N_episodes, max_episode_steps))
            n_occur_per_episode = np.ravel(all_occur.sum(axis=1))
            if freq_not_count:
                x = (n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:])[n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0] / \
                eplength[-n_last_episodes:][n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0]
            else:
                x = (n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:])[n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0]
            freq_occur_per_episode = x if len(x) else np.array([0]*(n_last_episodes if n_last_episodes else N_episodes))
        freq_arr += freq_occur_per_episode.flatten().tolist()
        n_occur_freq = len(freq_occur_per_episode)

        index_arr += [w_M / 2 + dp_index / N + exper_index * w_M]*n_occur_freq
        exper_arr += [exper_name] * n_occur_freq
        dp_arr += [detection_point] * n_occur_freq

        if barplot:
            ax.bar(w_M / 2 + dp_index / N + exper_index * w_M, freq_occur_per_episode.mean(), width=w_M, color=color[exper_index], align='center', label=exper_name)
    # print(freq_arr)
    
    if not barplot:
        df_freq = pd.DataFrame(zip(freq_arr, exper_arr, dp_arr), columns=[y_label, 'Experiments', 'Detection point names'])
        sns.violinplot(x='Detection point names', y=y_label, hue='Experiments', data=df_freq, widths=w_M,
        showmeans=True, showextrema=True, showmedians=False, # quantiles=[0.25, 0.75],
        points=100, bw_method=None)
    else:
        ax.set_ylabel(f"Last {n_last_episodes} "*(n_last_episodes != 0) + (not n_last_episodes)*"All "+ "epsiodes frequency")
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(plt.FixedLocator(np.linspace(0, 1, N+1)[:-1] + w_N/2))
        ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FixedFormatter(dp_names))
        ax.xaxis.set_minor_locator(plt.FixedLocator(np.linspace(0, 1, N*M+1))) # - w_M/2))
        ax.xaxis.set_minor_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda val, tick_number: exper_names[(tick_number - 1) % M].split('-')[1].split('.')[0]))
        ax.tick_params(axis='x', pad=30)
        plt.setp( ax.xaxis.get_minorticklabels(), rotation=45, ha='left')

    ax.set_ylabel(f"Last {n_last_episodes} "*(n_last_episodes != 0) + (not n_last_episodes)*"All "+ f"epsiodes {y_label.lower()}")
    ax.autoscale(tight=True)
    plt.ylim(bottom=-0.1*ax.get_ylim()[1])


    handles, labels = plt.gca().get_legend_handles_labels()
    by_label = dict(zip(labels, handles))
    ax.legend(by_label.values(), by_label.keys(), frameon=False)

    _ = fig.suptitle(f"{y_label} of triggers per episode with max episode length {max_episode_steps}")

def seaborn_barplot(cur_expers, include_dps=False, first_occur=False, freq_not_count=False, n_last_episodes=0, color = None):
    """Visualize results of experiments via maplotlib barlinplot"""

    detection_points_npz = {}
    for gymid in cur_expers:
        for date in cur_expers[gymid]:
            checkpoint_dir = os.path.join(log_dir, gymid, date)
            detection_points_npz[gymid + '.' + date] = np.load(os.path.join(checkpoint_dir, 'training',
                                                                            'detection_points_results.npz'))
    detection_point_names = set()
    detection_points_indices = {}
    for exper in detection_points_npz:
        for k in detection_points_npz[exper].keys():
            ht_dp_name, csr_index_type = '_'.join(k.split('_')[:-1]), k.split('_')[-1]
            if not include_dps and "dp" in ht_dp_name.lower():
                continue
            detection_point_names |= {ht_dp_name}
            detection_points_indices[exper + '.' + ht_dp_name] = detection_points_indices.get(exper + '.' + ht_dp_name, dict())
            detection_points_indices[exper + '.' + ht_dp_name].update({csr_index_type: detection_points_npz[exper][k]})

    dp_names, exper_names = sorted(list((detection_point_names))), sorted(list(detection_points_npz.keys()))

    # sns.set(style="darkgrid", color_codes=True) # 
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = plt.subplot(111)

    N, M = len(dp_names), len(exper_names)
    w_N = 1/N
    w_M = w_N/M


    for exper_ht_dp_name in detection_points_indices:
        # construct axes in fig, and log its index (i, j) inside axes
        gymid, date, detection_point = exper_ht_dp_name.split('.')
        exper_name = gymid + '.' + date
        exper_index, dp_index = exper_names.index(exper_name), dp_names.index(detection_point)
        
        indices = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['indices']
        indptr = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['indptr']
        eplength = detection_points_indices[exper_ht_dp_name]['eplength']
        n_nonzero, N_episodes = len(indices), len(indptr) - 1
        
        # n_episodes x 50
        all_occur = scipy.sparse.csr_matrix(([True] * n_nonzero, indices, indptr), 
                                            shape=(N_episodes, max_episode_steps))

        n_occur_per_episode = np.ravel(np.array(all_occur.sum(axis=1)))
        # only episodes which have nonzero inclusions
        if freq_not_count:
            freq_occur_per_episode = (n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:])[n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0] / \
                eplength[-n_last_episodes:][n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0]
        else:
            freq_occur_per_episode = (n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:])[n_occur_per_episode[-n_last_episodes:] > 0]
        freq_occur_per_episode = freq_occur_per_episode if len(freq_occur_per_episode) else [0]*n_epis
        ax.bar(w_M / 2 + dp_index / N + exper_index * w_M, freq_occur_per_episode.mean(), width=w_M, color=color[exper_index], align='center', label=exper_name)

    ax.set_ylabel(f"Last {n_last_episodes} "*(n_last_episodes != 0) + (not n_last_episodes)*"All "+ "epsiodes frequency")
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(plt.FixedLocator(np.linspace(0, 1, N+1)[:-1] + w_N/2))
    ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FixedFormatter(dp_names))
    ax.xaxis.set_minor_locator(plt.FixedLocator(np.linspace(0, 1, N*M+1))) # - w_M/2))
    ax.xaxis.set_minor_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda val, tick_number: exper_names[(tick_number - 1) % M].split('-')[1].split('.')[0]))
    ax.tick_params(axis='x', pad=30)
    plt.setp( ax.xaxis.get_minorticklabels(), rotation=45, ha='left')

    ax.autoscale(tight=True)


    handles, labels = plt.gca().get_legend_handles_labels()
    by_label = dict(zip(labels, handles))
    ax.legend(by_label.values(), by_label.keys(), frameon=False)

    _ = fig.suptitle(f"Frequency of triggers per episode with max episode length {max_episode_steps}")

    freq_occur_per_episode = n_occur_per_episode / detection_points_indices[name]['eplength']
    ax.plot(np.arange(len(n_occur_per_episode)), freq_occur_per_episode, label=detection_point)
    ax.set_xlabel("Episode")
    ax.set_ylabel("Frequency")

    eplength = len(detection_points_indices[name]['eplength'])
    ax.set_xlim(0, eplength)
    ax.set_title(gymid + '.' + date)
    extraxticks = [len(detection_points_indices[name]['eplength'])]
    ax.set_xticks(list(ax.get_xticks()) + extraxticks)
    ax.legend()
